726564f-a.title: Queens: Farrington Street - 32nd Avenue
726564f-a.text:
Farrington Street (foreground),at the S.W. corner of Thirty-
second Ave. (right), formerly Myrtle Ave., showing the 2. Roe house
in 1873. John Walsh was the occupant about 1900.
July 1923.
Eucene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
